ating extragalactic RSGs\nfrom foreground giants than mid-IR selection criteria, however the mid-IR\nselection criteria are useful for identifying dusty stars in the Local Group.\nThis work serves as a basis for further investigation of the newly discovered\ndusty massive stars and their host galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2015 20:15:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-18"}
