 formalism can also be\nutilized for determination of the effective exchange constant and magnetic\ncorrelations for itinerant magnetic systems, in general in a novel way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2015 04:33:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2015 09:57:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 23 Jul 2016 08:25:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-21"}
